2.14	Bad_Girls_(Buffy_the_Vampire_Slayer)	Bad Girls (Buffy the Vampire Slayer)	"Bad Girls" is episode 14 of season 3 of the television series Buffy the Vampire Slayer. It is written by Doug Petrie and directed by Michael Lange, it was originally broadcast on February 9, 1999 on the WB network. In "Bad Girls", Buffy gets a new Watcher, and Faith lures Buffy into reckless abandon.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/8/82/Buffy_3x14.jpg
